content.rendered:
Let’s start a movement. CompliMOVEment.

Bringing other girls down, only brings you down. Instead of using hurtful words, share your inner beauty- your kindness with those around you; it will radiate. Once you start spreading your love, it will affect more people than you will even realize, AND help with your own self-love.

So make an effort to compliment someone today. It will go a long way:)
